subject: Marathon Running
Olympic Games (2012)
lead_paragraph: Tiki Gelana of Ethiopia ran the second half of the race more than three minutes faster than the first, finishing in 2:23:7. The Americans Shalane Flanagan and Kara Goucher were 10th and 11th.
